interface userAuthProps {
  token: string
  username: string
  password: string
  address?: string
  nickname?: string
  tel?: string
  email?: string
  gender?: 'M' | 'F'
}

const userState: userAuthProps = {
  token: '',
  username: '',
  password: '',
}

interface changeUserState {}

function userAuth(state: userAuthProps = userState, action) {
  switch (action.type) {
    case 'LOGIN':
      return
    case 'REGISTER':
      return
    case 'SET_PROFILE':
      return
    case 'LOGOUT':
      return
    default:
      return state
  }
}
export default userAuth
